# Local dev value below. In production this REQUIRES a real value — the API
# is deployed as its own separate Render service (see root README.md →
# "Deploying to Render"), so there's no same-origin fallback to rely on. Set
# this at build time (wherever the frontend is hosted) to the deployed API's
# exact URL, e.g. VITE_API_URL="https://truvi-api.onrender.com"
VITE_API_URL="http://localhost:5000"

# Note: project-map "Auto-locate from address" now uses OpenStreetMap's free
# Nominatim geocoder (see client/src/lib/geocoding.ts) — no API key, no Google
# Cloud billing. There is nothing to configure here for the map.
